# [Other](scalate-embedding-guide.html)
</div>
<div class="right" markdown="1">
Don't see your favorite web framework on the list?  Then, take a look at the [Scalate Embedding Guide](scalate-embedding-guide.html) and see if you can be the first to add Scalate support to your favorite framework.
